    <div class="content">
        <p>
            Fysio Denmark is a leading provider of physiotherapy services in Denmark. 
            We are committed to providing the highest quality care to our patients. 
            Our team of experienced physiotherapists use the latest techniques and equipment 
            to help you achieve the best possible health outcomes.
            </p>
        <p>FysioDanmark A-Phys is a modern healthcare center that offers a wide range of healthcare services. As a patient or training member, you can get the whole body around under the same roof and you can combine treatment and training.</p>
            
           <p> With us, you will find the best in physiotherapy, exercise, sports and health gathered in one place, and we can therefore offer you a personal and specialized course, whether you are a patient or a training member. We attach great importance to the course of treatment being adapted precisely to your needs and functional level, and both high professionalism and discretion are a matter of course.</p>
            
            <p>It is important to us that you have a good experience and feel safe and respected when you are with us. Service is therefore not just something we talk about, but something we provide and we are constantly practicing to improve.</p>
            
           <p> A-Fys is a family-owned house for physics and health. Physiotherapist Lene Abildhauge started her 'clinic' in 1980, which has since become Solrød's largest treatment center and fitness centre.</p>
            
           <p> Today, the house is run by daughter Jo Abildhauge and son Mark Abildhauge.
            
            <p>The heart of the house beats for the high level of professionalism and expertise together with the community. A community carried by the 'A-Fys spirit', which we call the atmosphere in the house. The security, trust and care that means there is room for everyone.</p>
        Contact us today to book your appointment.
